title: Willkommen in Bremen
description: Wolfgang Schefer is getting promoted and should take the command of the Bremen navy site. The whole family moves to Bremen, and after the arrival, mother Sybille is revealing to their children that she'll work on the same school that's visited by Felix, Jenny, Moritz an Alex. But the kids are not as enthusiastic as expected ...

title: Nichtraucher, sportlich
description: Moritz is mad at his teacher Mrs. Schmalz: first he receives a 5 (=E) for the interpretation of a Wolfgang Borchert poem as a "one night stand", then the finds out that he's a diabetic and tells this to the whole class. Moritz seeks revenge and finds his chance soon when Heike Schmalz leaves a newspaper on her table where some lonely hearts ads are marked. Moritz and his friend Jakob create an ad which must attract her attention ...

title: Die Mafia
description: Alex wins a baseball jacket from Moritz. When he's proudly wearing his new piece of clothing the next day in school, he gets attacked and the jacket is stolen. Moritz tries to play the investigator, but he gets bashed in front of Benitas house. Time for another plan of the Schefer family and their friends ...
